  "title": "约束与排错",
  "description": "使用 Codex + Anydocs MCP 时最常见的约束与故障排查点。",
  "tags": [
    "reference",
    "troubleshooting"
  ],
  "status": "published",
  "updatedAt": "2026-03-19T00:00:00.000Z",
  "content": {
    "version": 1,
    "blocks": [
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "id": "block-1",
        "level": 1,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "约束与排错"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "block-2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "最常见的几条约束："
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "id": "block-3",
        "style": "bulleted",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "element-3-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "`projectRoot` 必须显式传入"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-4-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "`lang` 必须是项目已启用语言"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-5-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "`page_update` 不能改 `status`"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-6-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "如果页面发布需要审批，`page_set_status` 到 `published` 可能被拒绝"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "block-7",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "遇到报错时的处理方式："
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "id": "block-8",
        "style": "numbered",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "element-8-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "先保留错误原文，尤其是 `rule` 与 `remediation`"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-9-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "回到 `project_open` 或 `project_validate` 确认项目状态"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-10-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "用 `page_get` / `page_find` 确认目标页面是否真的存在"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-11-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "不要为了“先做完”而绕过 MCP 直接修改 JSON"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "block-12",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "如果你把这些规则写进 `AGENTS.md`，Codex 的行为会稳定很多。"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
